headline: Elevance Health (NYSE:ELV) Faces Shareholder Proposal on Diversity and Inclusion Reporting
summary: Elevance Health (NYSE:ELV) recently faced shareholder proposals aimed at increasing transparency in its diversity, equity, and inclusion initiatives.
